column5: How mentally demanding was the task? (Mental demand)
column6: How physically demanding was the task? (Physical demand)
column7: How much time pressure did you feel due to rate or pace at which the tasks occurred? (Temporal demand)
column8: How successful do you think you were in accomplishing the task that you were asked to? (Performance)

column10: How irritated, stressed, and annoyed were you? (Frustration Level)
